# Changelog

> Example request

```http
GET https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/jobs HTTP/1.1
X-Api-Version : 20161108
```

```shell
curl -X "GET" "https://api.teamtailor.com/v1/jobs" \
     -H "X-Api-Version: 20161108"
```

### 2018-11-05 *Non breaking update*
 * Signed URLs to [Uploads](#uploads) files are valid for 1 minute.

### 2018-09-17 *Non breaking update*
 * Filter [Jobs](#jobs) by status `archived`.

### 2018-07-17 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `created_at` field to `jobs`

### 2018-05-31 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `send-default-reply` attribute to [job-applications](#job-applications)

### 2018-05-11 *Non breaking update*
 * [Picked questions](#picked-questions) endpoint.
 * Added  `picked-questions` resource to [jobs](#jobs)
 * Added `name_requirement`, `resume_requirement`, `cover_letter_requirement`, `phone_requirement` attributes to [jobs](#jobs)

### 2018-05-22 *Non breaking update*
 * New [User](#users) attributes for GDPR/data retention notifications. (`notification-removal-request` and `notification-gdpr-digest`)

### 2018-04-26 *Non breaking update*
 * [List questions](#list-questions) endpoint.

### 2018-04-19 *Non breaking update*
 * Add user notification settings attributes to the user object.
 * Add TeamMembership object to enable index, view, create and destroy actions on hiring team members.

### 2018-04-05 *Non breaking update*
 * Add `colleagues` relation to `jobs` (lists `users` related to the job ad).

### 2018-04-04 *Non breaking update*
 * Add `external-application-url` field to `jobs`.

### 2018-03-02 *Non breaking update*
 * Filter [candidates](#candidates) by `locations`.

### 2018-02-13 *Non breaking update*
 * New resource [Uploads](#uploads).
 * Added `uploads` resource to [candidates](#candidates).
 * Filter [candidates](#candidates) by `connected`, `department` and `role`.

### 2018-01-25 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `locations` resource to [candidates](#candidates).
 * Filter [users](#users) by `email`.
 * Can update `email` attribute on [users](#users).

### 2018-01-16 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `create` and `update` actions to [users](#users).
 * Set `picture` to [jobs](#jobs) by passing an URL to a picture.

### 2017-10-31 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `tags` to [jobs](#jobs).

### 2017-09-06 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `apply-button-text` attribute to [jobs](#jobs).

### 2017-03-15 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `single-line` attribute to [questions](#questions).

### 2017-03-10 *Non breaking update*
 * Added `changed_stage_at` to [job applications](#job-applications).
 * Made it possible to filter on `stage-type` when listing [job applications](#job-applications).

### 2017-02-23 *Non breaking update*

